Russia to Impose More Restrictions on Brazil Meat, Valor Says

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-08-02T12:12:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-02/russia-to-impose-more-restrictions-on-brazil-meat-valor-says.html
Russia will impose “additional
restrictions” on meat imports from  Brazil  that don’t meet
sanitary standards,  Valor Economico  reported, citing
unidentified Brazilian government authorities.  Russia has temporarily banned meat imports from Brazil
since June 15.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in  Sao Paulo  at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 